g><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"189b391ddc3180819ede241a37535fa7db7ab52c","tid":1183172,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acfbe70a7cb639f46bfe765382c4bcf1128ad03f","tid":1183172,"uid":25019,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:25:55.000Z","msg":"支那野點柒都好 未理由咁樣出事 一定有心玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:27:46.000Z","msg":"廢囉on9"},{"pid":"ea3e0f478173cde40b4193d593153c71ac92d593","tid":1183172,"uid":25019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"189b391ddc3180819ede241a37535fa7db7ab52c","tid":1183172,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acfbe70a7cb639f46bfe765382c4bcf1128ad03f","tid":1183172,"uid":25019,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:25:55.000Z","msg":"支那野點柒都好 未理由咁樣出事 一定有心玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:27:46.000Z","msg":"廢囉on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"廢還廢都唔會冇試用過啦"},{"pid":"9f53532b43bf2724407802c5c8e5d4c9ea475610","tid":1183172,"uid"